    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear 8,000 RPM powerband. The chassis has been enhanced with documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed polyurethane bushings to maintain factory suspension geometry under lateral load. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and underpinnings are dialed for immediate performance use.",
