    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride of ownership, offering a reliable and premium driving experience. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is pristine and smoke-free; the leather upholstery is soft and well-conditioned, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic systems, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment suite, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a full brake inspection completed last month. This is a turnkey vehicle, ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required.",
